VARIABLE CABINET

NUMBER 751
NAME Dane's Castle, Sanctum
*DESCRIPTION_START
Blocks of granite meticulously burnished to a shine make up the walls of this stately room with a petrified uquart floor. An ornate wall sconce is the focus of attention from where it hangs above a massive mirmach desk and enormous ursine-skin chair that looks out the window. A large portrait of a Drakin Warrior with a huge greatsword mounted next to it adorns the North wall. A keg sits in a corner opposite a huge oak door leading out.
*DESCRIPTION_END
INDOOR_FLOOR
DARKNESS
