*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The spigot has been fashioned to look like an ursine head.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The huge oak door leading back to pleasant street has a latch on it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
The portrait on the wall is of a distinguished looking Drakin warrior with jet
black scales and fiery red eyes on a battlefield. He has a ripplingly muscled,
fighters' physique, and is the largest drakin you've ever seen! In one hand he
easily wields a jeweled greatsword with his clan-name engraved into the blade.
The ground surrounding the warrior is littered with the remains of those
foolish enough to advance upon him. The placard at the bottom reads:
Nathaniel Stonebreaker -- Patriarch to the Clan Stonebreaker.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
The wall sconce has been crafted by a master to resemble a glittering black dragon in flight. The dragon has diamond sharp claws, magnificient wings, and it's eyes gleam with a mystical intelligence. It's wings are open as it catches a gus t of wind. A gout of white flame is issuing from it's gaping maw lighting the room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
It looks like a big desk.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
It is a wingback chair is covered with the hide of a huge ursine, and would be a befitting throne for royalty. The spine of the chair is encrusted rubies, sapphires, diamonds and emeralds. Sturdy handrests extend from each side of the chair, ending with the claws of the ursine.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 6
The great keg is made from an unknown metal, and has spigot extruding from one end. On a platform immediately below the tap is an empty mug.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 7
XXX
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 8
A huge bejeweled greatsword with the name "Stonebreaker" engraved on the blade is mounted on the wall in this place of honor. The blade is razor-sharp, and appears capable of slicing an ursine in two with one swing. The hilt has been wound with rashasaka gut for an unbreakable grip. The pommel of the greatsword is fashioned into a skull with rubies for eyes.
*DESCRIPTION_END
