NAME Tower room
*DESCRIPTION_START
A large bay window allows sunlight to fill this circular room at any time of day. Unusual technological artifacts hang about the walls. A black metal desk and matching straight-back chair face the window at an oblique angle. Away from the window but still facing out, a large sofa and several scattered pillows atop a thick rug form a sort of comfortable viewing area. From behind the sofa, the face from a portrait gaze out at you.
*DESCRIPTION_END
