The wall is covered with intesting technolgical artifacts. Of particular note is a working phaser, and a set of ancient decorative scrolls depicting bloody scenes from the Technomancy War. Lanterns are evenly spaced along the wall to provide light in the night hours.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
The design of the desk is very clean, almost cubic. It has A front panel and two side below its smooth shiny top so that the entire inside is open. There is a small return tucked underneath one side, and it has a tiny drawer.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
The chair matches the desk in its sort of cubic style. It has a small square, lightly padded gray seat. The back of the chair is constructed of eight metal rods that extend from a base at the floor up to about shoulder height where they flare out slightly.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
The sofa is of simple elegant construction. It is a long rectangle with a low back and arms. Firm square seat and back cushions line its interior where a few throw pillows of white and black have better scattered to break up the simple lines.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
Its just a big soft pillow inviting you to come and snuggle up with it on the floor.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 6
The plush threads of the large rug combine to form a depiction of warriors battling a dragon.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 7
You see a solitary figure standing in a smoking wasteland surrounded by the shattered technological remains of an earlier era. His clothes are tattered and he carries nothing but a small shiny instrument.
*DESCRIPTION_END
