NUMBER 753
NAME Cyrano's residence, front yard
DAY_LIGHT
FOREST
*DESCRIPTION_START
You are in the spacious front yard of Cyrano's residence. Great care has spent
arranging the garden which is located to either side of the brick path leading
from the gate to the townhouse. Several large leafy elm trees are dispersed
throughout the garden. On the western side of the garden is a small fountain
with a mermaid for a centerpiece. Two benches are neatly arranged, on opposite
sides of the fountain. To the south is the gate leading out to Pleasant
Street. A path leads from the gate to the front door of the townhouse.
*DESCRIPTION_END
