INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
Herein lies a comfortable living and dining area with a huge vaulted ceiling
and floors made of sturdy mirmach polished to a dull shine. Near the center of
the room rests a massive circular stone fireplace. Surrounding the fireplace
are an assortment of comfortable overstuffed arm chairs, including Cyrano's
favorite brown leather reading chair. Near the southern wall, you see a small
wooden dining table with four matching highback chairs. Nearly out of sight,
you glimpse a small stove, cutting table and cabinet overflowing with
kitchen utensils. A large crimson tapestry covers the northern wall
depicting five regal figures sitting about a round table filled with
food and drink. A stairway is located against the western wall next
to the doorway leading out.
*DESCRIPTION_END
