*DESCRIPTION_START
The front rooms of this simple yet elegant home flow together without walls
for an open, spacious feeling. Conveniently placed next to the tidy kitchen
is a long dining room table surrounded by high-backed chairs. The other side
of the room features a large, comfortable sofa and easy chair adjoining a
coffee table and fur rug. Bookshelves holding tomes and tools related to
healing, alchemy, psionics and weaving line the richly appointed study to the
left of the brick fireplace, while a sewing area occupies the corner to its
right.
*DESCRIPTION_END
