*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
These bookshelves are filled with many volumes concerning a wide variety of
topics. Ancient tomes about magic sit side by side with even more ancient works
about technology. The shelves also contain many books about both obscure and
major religions, including one on the mysterious Drakin religion. History,
politics, various philosophies, and all the natural and physical sciences are
represented as well. The majority of them have worn bindings and dog-eared
pages.
*DESCRIPTION_END
