*DESCRIPTION_START
The large area is covered with a hardwood slat floor. One side
appears to be the kitchen and dinning room area with a table and
chairs over a colorful braided rug acting as the focus. A large
cauldron filled with mulled cider fills the large fireplace. Shelves
filled with various herbs, spices, and poultices take up most of one
wall. A metal contraption with a long handle, used for obtaining
water, sits next to a large porcelain basin set into a counter.
The other side of the room contains a soft leather couch facing
a large picture window that views the river. Three comfortable
overstuffed chairs are interspersed about the room. There is a snow
white, plush carpet lying softly in front of a small fireplace.
Bookshelves containing volumes of literature, history, and magic line
the walls. A huge painting of a beautiful landscape hangs above the
couch. A spiral staircase leads to the upstairs room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
