NUMBER 774
NAME Samadhi cloud room
DEEPCAVE
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Your feet are supported by the mist-shrouded floor as though you walk across
the surface of a gently swaying sea, a yielding surface of unknown composition.
It really does feel as though you're walking through the cloud this chamber
is designed to resemble. At its heart is a formation of solidified mist in
the shape of an indistinct, comfortable bed. Gentle pastel shades of purple
and red drift through the billowing mists, providing just enough light to
see by. The ceiling above is a warm, dark spread of pinpoint stars on a
black background. Looking about you feel completely at peace.
*DESCRIPTION_END
