*DESCRIPTION_START
As you step into this warm cabin, a wonderful scent greets you, faintly
tugging at your memory. Shirred white curtains are pulled back from the
window, letting light in to glow softly against the light wood of the
walls. Many shades of greens mix for a pleasant effect in the rug and throw
pillows. At the opposite end of the room is the table and eating area. A
beautiful painting over the plush sofa draws your eye. Everything seems to
be in its place, but still comfortable and inviting. It is evident this is
someone's well loved Home. A stone fireplace and a cradle are here.
