*DESCRIPTION_START
Midnight blue and ivory colors decorate the room, creating a stunning
visual impact. The light colored fur rug seems to beckon your toes in
this restive and cozy room of the cabin. Centered against the back wall
of this spacious and well-lit room is a large bed with four high and
intricately carved rosewood posts. A mound of hand embroidered and
ribboned pillows lay casually on the bed. Nearby, a bookcase is filled
with books about weapons, magic, designing, jewelry and stories. Next to
the the huge closet a coatrack stands in the corner, with a kimono and a
little lace nightie flung over it. A rocking chair looks out the window
with a book laid open near it. At the end of the bed is a full length
chest with a padded tapestry cushion.
