NUMBER 3727
NAME Lexa and Destrar's place, bedroom
INDOOR_FLOOR
PARTIAL_DARKNESS
*DESCRIPTION_START
Soft lighting suffuses the room from an indeterminate source, and the air
shimmers with a radiance that imparts a warm glow to everything in it.
Iridescent pale peach lace floats from a hardwood frame to canopy the
luxurious bed, piled with silks and furs, and curtains the windows that lead
out to a small back garden. Framed prints of delicately detailed wildflowers
and animals are arranged in a pattern on the walls, framing the door that
leads back out into the living room.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;door
