*DESCRIPTION_START
The lighting is diffused and softened by a fine gossamer canopy above the
beautifully carved fourposter bed that sits in the center of the room. Soft
curtains of the same finespun gossamer hang in a window that overlooks the
backyard. A polished hardwood rack displays Wolfbane's weapons and matching
bureaus stand side by side opposite the door. A filmy negligee is casually
tossed on an upholstered bench that sits before a brass dressing table.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
Beautifully carved rose filled vines wrap themselves around the four columns
that support a gossamer canopy. The elegant curve of the eagle's wings are
offset by the intricately carved forpiece in the shape of a proud wolf's head.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
Behind the glass-fronted rack light glints off the blades of two crossed
weapons: an albescent longsword and an albescent papenheimer, each bearing
the crest of the Crimson Band engraved on the pommel. They rest in elegant
splendor, displayed against the deep crimson velvet that lines the interior
of the rack.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
