Your reflection in the mirror is framed by a hazy nimbus of reflected light.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
Carved into the front of the bureau is a howling wolf silhouetted against
outspread eagle's wings. The top of the dresser is bare except for a framed
portrait of Sun and Wolfbane on their wedding day.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
The front of the bureau is carved with a lovingly detailed white rose, kissed
with tiny glints of gold that hint at sun reflecting drops of dew. Carefully
arranged on top of the bureau are a number of trinkets: some jewelry, a
spellbook, and a beautifully carved music box.
*DESCRIPTION_END

