ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The walls, floor, and ceiling of this spacious room are misty and hard
to focus on.  The size and shape of the room are more easily
determined by the wall hangings, furniture, and a large blue rug with
gold trim that covers the floor.  A large chandelier lights  the room
with a warm glow.  There is a comfortable looking sofa of gold and
blue silk, a table with two chairs, and other small items  that give
the room a cozy atmosphere.  There is a curtain to the east and an
archway to the north.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
At first glance, the royal blue appears to be a solid weave, but as you move around the room, the shifting play of light reveals a hidden pattern of desert roses that shimmer and shift into clouds as you watch. The warm glow of the gold fringe suffuses the soft blue like sunlight on the water.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 6
Faceted teardrops cut of fine crystal catch and reflect the light, suffusing it with soft color and softening any harsh edges. The chandelier seems to hang suspended at just the right height with no visible support at all, and beyond it, the ceiling is impossible to make out clearly.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 7
The finely woven tapestry depicts a sunset desert after a rare rainstorm. The cacti are softened with shades of deep emerald, and topped with bright flowers in pink and yellow and red. Here and there a deep red desert rose blooms, and sage sends out tiny tendrils of green to carpet the ground.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
