*DESCRIPTION_START
A large brass bed takes center stage in this room, the fluffy pastels of the
down comforter mimicking a springtime sky. A small white desk stands to one
side, with a simple wooden chair upholstered with pale blue and white
cushions is drawn up before it. A portrait of a purple butterfly hangs on
one insubstantial wall, the background fading so it seems suspended in
midair. By day, the misty walls are suffused and warmed by sunlight, and at
