*DESCRIPTION_START
A short distance down the path you find a small log cabin nestled in a
grove of trees. As you approach the door you encounter a feeling of
familiarity...a sense that you have been here before. There is a
peacefullness and gentleness that seems to emanate from all directions.
A small waterfall pours into a crystal clear pool which supplies a stream
running through the area. The water, fed from deep within the shartans is
comfortably warm all year long.
*DESCRIPTION_END
