between a young human and a young drakin, both wielding drakin
weapons. Closer examination shows a glint of amusment in the
older drakins eyes and possibly a hint of pride. The faces of
both youths betray no hint of anger, but show an intensity of
concentration only found in long hours of training.
*DESCRIPTION_END
