NUMBER 1694
DEEPCAVE
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL
*DESCRIPTION_START
You pass through the waterfall to find room carved into the hillside. It is
warm here but surprisingly comfortable. The walls are bare except
for shelves and hooks carved into the stone. There are soft dry towels on the
shelves and soft cotton robes of various sizes on the hooks. The floor is
smooth and covered with a thick layer of snowy white furs. there is a faint
scent of violets in the air.
*DESCRIPTION_END
