*DESCRIPTION_START
Deep green velvet curtains frame a large window that looks out on the street
below. Soft lighting picks up the rich colors in the luxurious carpet that
covers the hardwood floor, and spotlights the large colorful map above the
hearth. A comfortable overstuffed sofa sits opposite the fireplace, flanked
by two upholstered chairs. The mahogany paneling and oakframed woodwork
gleam with warm highlights. An oak door leads back into the hallway.
*DESCRIPTION_END
