ITEM 3 65 OPEN UNLOCKED VAL2=1579
*DESCRIPTION_START
Oak paneling in a shade darker than the floor covers the walls of this small
room, freshly cleaned and gleaming with warm highlights. The brick hearth is
swept and scrubbed, and an iron grate supports three thick logs ready to be
lit. Although the floor appears freshly sanded, there is still a dark stain
that has seeped into the wood, resisting all efforts to remove it.
An oak door leads back out into the hallway.
*DESCRIPTION_END
